# Automation Pipeline

## Agent Skills (`.cursor/skills/`)

| Skill | Trigger | What It Does |
|---|---|---|
| `blog-writer` | "write a blog post", "draft a tutorial" | Full blog post + quiz creation following style guide |
| `content-leverage-engine` | "repurpose", "social posts", "leverage content" | Generates LinkedIn, Twitter/X, Instagram, newsletter from any content |
| `staff-prep-daily` | "today's tasks", "daily prep" | Daily study plan from 60-day Staff Engineer prep schedule |

## Content Pipeline (Chained)

```
blog-writer (steps 1-5)
  → Write MDX post + quiz JSON
  → Verify quality checklist
  ↓
content-leverage-engine (step 6, auto-triggered)
  → Generate: LinkedIn post, X thread, Instagram carousel + reel, newsletter
  → Save X thread to content/blog/drafts/.social/{slug}-x.json (draft)
  ↓
publish-post (when user publishes)
  → Move draft to published, set draft: false
  → Post X thread from .social/{slug}-x.json
  → Post to LinkedIn
  → Remove social draft file
```

## Scripts (`scripts/`)

| Script | npm command | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `post-to-x.ts` | `npm run post-x` | Post tweet or thread to X via API v2 |
| `post-to-linkedin.ts` | `npm run post-linkedin` | Post to LinkedIn |
| `publish-post.ts` | `npm run publish-post -- <slug>` | Publish one draft + post X + LinkedIn |
| `publish-scheduled.ts` | `npm run publish-posts` | Publish scheduled drafts + post X + LinkedIn |
| `list-scheduled.ts` | `npm run list-scheduled` | List posts scheduled for publishing |

## X Posting Modes

- `--slug <slug>` — Auto-generate announcement tweet from a published blog post
- `--file <path.json>` — Post a thread from JSON (`{ "mode": "thread", "tweets": [...] }`)
- `--dry-run` — Preview without posting

## Environment Variables (`.env`, gitignored)

- `X_API_KEY`, `X_API_SECRET`, `X_ACCESS_TOKEN`, `X_ACCESS_TOKEN_SECRET` — X API v2 OAuth 1.0a
- `LINKEDIN_ACCESS_TOKEN`, `LINKEDIN_AUTHOR_URN` — LinkedIn posting
- `GARMIN_EMAIL`, `GARMIN_PASSWORD` — Running data sync
